顯示範圍：第筆 論文書目資料
顯示格式：全部欄位
      共&nbsp20&nbsp筆




------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
      第 1 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0026-0209201312300600


論文名稱(中文) 
      
應用「台灣地震災害損失評估系統」模擬2010年甲仙地震及旗山斷層破裂對高雄市之影響


論文名稱(英文) 
      
Applying " Taiwan Earthquake Loss Estimation System" to simulate influences of the 2010 Jiasian, Taiwan, earthquake and the Chishan fault ruptures to Kaohsiung City, Taiwan


校院名稱
成功大學


系所名稱(中)
地球科學系專班


系所名稱(英)
Department of Earth Sciences (on the job class)


學年度
101


學期
2


出版年
102


研究生(中文)
李博閔


學號
L47001039


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2013-07-30


論文頁數
99頁


口試委員
指導教授-樂鍇‧祿璞崚岸
口試委員-饒瑞鈞
口試委員-景國恩



關鍵字(中)
甲仙地震台灣地震損失評估系統旗山斷層地震災害地震防災


關鍵字(英)
Jiashian earthquakeTELESChishan faultearthquake disasterearthquake disaster prevention


學科別分類



中文摘要
台灣位於環太平洋地震帶上，時時刻刻受到地震之威脅。高雄市位於台灣西南部，自從2010年12月25日高雄縣、市合併後，幅員面積廣大且境內有小崗山、旗山、潮州斷層等活動斷層，若遭受強地震振動，恐導致難以估計之人命及財產損傷。    2010年03月04日發生96人受傷及龐大財產損失之甲仙地震 (ML=6.4)，最大震度達6級 (395 gal)，此地震為近年來高雄地區發生規模較大之地震。本研究利用國家地震工程研究中心發展「台灣地震損失評估系統」(Taiwan Earthquake Loss Estimation System，TELES)，使用TELES以2010年甲仙地震震源資料當參數，模擬點震源、面震源地震PGA分佈圖，並由248個地震測站資料繪出測站PGA分佈圖，由強地震觀測網測站PGA分佈圖發現震央位置PGA與地震參數設定為面震源之PGA分佈情形較為符合。    探討旗山斷層破裂發生芮氏規模7之地震，模擬建築物倒塌、人員傷亡情形：結果為建築物倒塌情形因三民區、左營區建築物分佈廣且高樓多，模擬結果最為嚴重；人命傷亡情形因人口密度高，模擬結果以楠梓區、仁武區、大社區、三民區最為嚴重。因此，整體防災考量以高雄市三民區為優先規劃，提出應變中心設置、人命搜救、緊急醫療部署、收容中心安置等4項建議事項，以期供高雄市政府等相關機關參考應用。


英文摘要
Situated on the Circum-Pacific seismic belt, Taiwan has constantly suffered from earthquakes. Kaohsiung City, second largest city in Taiwan, has several active faults such as the Hsiaokangshan, Chishan, Chaochou faults. If a large earthquake strikes the city, it will cause severe damages to structures and kill numerous people.On March 4, 2010, a magnitude 6.4 earthquake (ML=6.4, PGA = 395gal), occurred in Jiashian District of Kaohsiung City, has been the largest earthquake in Kaohsiung in the history. The 2010 Jiashian earthquake caused 96 people injured and damages to several buildings. In this study, we use "Taiwan Earthquake Loss Estimation System (TELES)" which is developed by the "National Center for Research on Earthquake Engineering (NCREE)" to simulate the ground motions and evaluate the patterns of the damages if the Chishan fault ruptures. According to the records of the 248 seismic stations by the "Taiwan Strong Motion Instrumentation Program Network (TSMIP)" of the 2010 Jiashian earthquake, the comparisons suggest that it is more suitable to assume a plane source than a point source of the earthquake.We simulate the damage patterns and casualty scenarios of a magnitude 7 earthquake occurring on the Chishan fault. The severest collapse zones of the buildings are in Sanmin and Zuoying Districts because of more widely distributed high-rise buildings. There are more casualties in Nanzih, Renwu, Dashu and Sanmin Districts because of their higher population density. Therefore, considering the respect of disaster prevention, we should pay more attentions to those districts, especially to Sanmin District. So we bring up four advices to Kaohsiung City Government, including how to set up Emergency Operation Center, Search and Rescue Life Command Troop, Emergency Medical Deployment Team and Refugee Shelter Accommodator, and expect that these plans could be offered those relevant authorities.


