口試委員
指導教授-吳銘志
共同指導教授-紀文榮
口試委員-鍾廣吉
口試委員-蔡金郎
口試委員-謝英宗



關鍵字(中)
澐水溪指示化石的最早出現基準面指示化石的最後存在基準面生物地層


關鍵字(英)
Yunshui RiverIndex Fossils of the First Appearance Datum(FAD)Index Fossils of the Last Appearance Datum (LAD)biostratigraphic


學科別分類



中文摘要
澐水溪為八掌溪的支流，位於臺灣西南部嘉義縣中埔鄉內。澐水溪地質剖面位於以竹頭崎斷層與崙後斷層為界的西部外麓山帶。本研究應用超微化石之指示化石的最早出現基準面（FAD）和最後存在基準面（LAD），與應用指示化石所訂出來的超微化石帶及化石群，重新建立本區域生物地層層序。並進一步確定地層年代的有效性與連續性，和上新世與更新世（P/P）、中新世與上新世（M/P）在澐水溪剖面的位置。


英文摘要
The Yunshui River, being a tributary of Bazhang River, is located at Zhongpu Township of Chiayi County, southwest of Taiwan. The Yunshui River profile is sectioned within the outer western foothills of Taiwan, bounded by Zhutouqi Fault and Lun-Ho Fault. In this study, the Nannobiostratigraphs of the Yunshui River profile is established with Index Fossils of the First Appearance Datum (FAD) and the Last Appearance Datum (LAD). In addition, by implementing the Index fossils, the Standard Nannofossil Zonations, the Nannofossil Zonations, Fauna of Common Species were reestablished to identify the biostratigraphic chronological sequences of the region. Further more to check the effectiveness and continuity of the stratigraphic chronology as well as the location of Pliocene／Pleistocene (P/P) and Miocene／Pliocene (M/P) boundaries for the Yunshui River geologic profile.


論文目次
