Tainan Confucian templeChen YonghuaConfucian temple culture campusZheng family


學科別分類
學科別＞人文學＞語言文學



中文摘要
臺南孔廟因南明時的鄭氏家族退居臺灣而得以創建自陳永華之手，代表了臺灣儒家初始化，更因鄭氏家族在臺的一切建設由府城向外擴展，使臺南孔廟成為全臺教育的最高指導機構。但經過了清廷歷任來臺官吏的修建與改製，將陳永華依同安孔廟所建的臺南孔廟改為清代規模，將大量的師傅與建材運送來臺，完成今日所見臺南孔廟的大致樣貌，除了少數幾座建築因戰後的經費缺乏而未列入修復外，孔廟建築與珍物在日治時期受到以成書院的院生們與地方士紳的保護而得以留存。待臺南市政府依日治時期的都市計畫加上文化園區的概念，形成今日府城五大園區之首的「孔廟文化園區」，不僅有全臺古老具歷史意義的建築物在孔廟周邊，更將觀光與復古概念結合，舉辦如「祭孔、敬師」等各項活動。但實際觀察下，即可發現在臺南孔廟旁臺南市南門路上的友愛街口至府前路的路段中，經常出現人車爭道現象，一時的規劃不良造成今日許多用路人的不便與險象環生，連帶府中街也乏人問津，因此於本文第五章中提出因應之法。再將教育應用於孔廟，筆者提出一些平日即可舉辦的高中生校外參訪與競賽，使平日孔廟兼具教育性質與文化創意展示平臺。


英文摘要
Because the Tainan Confucian temple time Southern Ming's Zheng family steps down Taiwan, but can found hand of from the Chen Yonghua, has represented Taiwan Confucianist initialization, because the Zheng family expands outward in Taiwan's all constructions by the prefectural city, causes the Tainan Confucian temple to become the entire Taiwan education the highest instruction organization. But passed through the Qing government to successively hold the coming to Taiwan government official's construction and the remanufacture, according to changes the Qing Dynasty scale Chen Yonghua with the Tainan Confucian temple which the peaceful Confucian temple constructed, massive skilled workers and the building materials ship come to Taiwan, to complete see the Tainan Confucian temple today the approximate appearance, because the postwar funds lacked besides the minority several constructions has not included the repair, the Confucian temple construction and the rare things governed the time in the date to receive become academy's courtyard to live and the place gentry's protection, but could preserve. Waits the Tainan municipal government to govern the time according to the date the metropolis plan to add on the cultural campus the concept, forms today heads of the prefectural city five big campus “the Confucian temple culture campus”, not only has the entire Taiwan ancient historic importance building in the Confucian temple peripheral, will go sightseeing with restores the old the concept union, conducts like “offers a sacrifice to the hole, the respect teacher” and so on each activity. But under the actual observation, then discovered that nearby the Tainan Confucian temple south Taina in the method friendly affection intersection to the government office road ahead's road section, presents person Che frequently Zheng a phenomenon, the temporary plan bad creates many uses passer-by's inconveniencing today and is surrounded by perils, in the association government office the street also useless person asks about, therefore proposes in this article fifth chapter in accordance to it law. Will educate again applies in the Confucian temple, the author proposed some ordinary days then conducts the high-school student extracurricular visit and the competition, cause ordinary day the Confucian temple to have both the education nature and the cultural creativity demonstrate the platform.


