      第 4 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0026-0708201211113000


論文名稱(中文) 
      
臺南市幼托政策之研究-以仁德區公立幼兒園為例


論文名稱(英文) 
      
Research on the Integration Policy of Nursing & Kindergarten in Tainan-The Case of Rende District


校院名稱
成功大學


系所名稱(中)
政治經濟學研究所專班


系所名稱(英)
Graduate Institute of Political Economy


學年度
100


學期
2


出版年
101


研究生(中文)
楊惠朱


學號
u17991058


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2012-06-05


論文頁數
189頁


口試委員
指導教授-楊永年
口試委員-鄭邦鎮
口試委員-莊輝濤



關鍵字(中)
幼托整合政策臺南市仁德區


關鍵字(英)
The integration policy of preschool instituteThe Rende District of Tainan City


學科別分類



中文摘要
摘    要幼托整合是臺灣幼托政策史上的重大變革。臺南市政府在縣市合併周年時，配合中央政府進行幼托整合政策實施，使得臺南市幼托機構轉型及政策制度面臨兩次變革挑戰。本論文目的是藉由仁德區公立幼兒園在幼托政策早期階段性的實施過程進行研究，主要在思考如何提供幼兒及市民優質且平價的學前機會均等教育，保障不利條件幼兒，同時提高教保服務功能。主要研究內涵包括臺南市政府在縣市合併後至目前幼托整合的早期實施階段，政策的形成、規劃及執行如何？能否達到組織成員及家長滿意度，都是本研究主要探討的問題。本研究透過文獻分析法、深度訪談法及個案分析進行研究、分析、歸納。研究結果有以下八項發現：一、不利條件幼兒比較弱勢。二、學校附設幼兒園無法收托2至3歲幼兒。三、幼托政策子法與相關規定尚未完全訂出。四、教保服務人員專業知能需再提升。五、人員待遇福利標準不同。六、人力及設施設備相關經費尚未到位。七、幼兒園無法成為實習場所並不合理。八、考試用人短期間恐造成組織不穩定。根據前述研究發現，本論文提出以下八項建議：一、堅持政府照顧不利條件幼兒的決心。二、中央應儘速擬訂教保服務的配套措施。三、持續與利害關係人進行溝通。四、教保服務人員應朝專業體系方向發展。五、人員待遇應符合平等一致及信賴保護原則。六、中央專款補助以健全組織改善設施設備。七、暢通人員取得幼教師資格管道。八、考試採雙軌並進以維持組織基本穩定。


英文摘要
AbstractThe preschool integration policy is a major change in the history of childcare in Taiwan. Tainan City Government followed the integration policy of central government in 2011 after the merging between Tainan City and Tainan County governments in 2010. The purpose of this research is to investigate the policy implementation effectivenss for preschool education including issues of quality, equity, disadvantaged children. The focus is on the early integration policy formation, planning, and implementation in Tainan City. It also includes the satisfaction of the members of staffs and teachers of preschool institutes and parents of the students. The research methods include literature review, in-depth interview, and case study. There were eight research findings. First, the disadvantaged children were in disadvantaged position. Second, two to three years old children cannot be allowed to go to elementary schools. Third, the regulation of integration policy has not been finished. Fourth, the basic knowledge has to be improved for the preschool teachers. Fifth, the fringe benefits were different across different districts of Tainan City. Sixth, there were not enough human resources for preschool institutes to conduct the integrating policy. Seventh, it was not reasonable to prevent preschool institutes from practical trainings. The preschool institutes would be unstable during the period of hiring employees. There are eight suggestions for this research. First, governments have to deal with the issues of disadvantaged children. Second, central government has to form system policies and laws for the integration policy. Third, communication is necessary for policy stakeholders. Fourth, preschool teachers must receive have more professional trainings than before. Fifth, the salary of preschool teachers should be the same across different districts. Sixth, financing should be provided by the central government to improve the facilities of preschool institutes. Seventh, licensing should be conducted smoothly for the preschool teachers without licenses. Eighth, two systems of hiring new preschool teachers should bemaintained to ensure the stability.


論文目次
