215頁


口試委員
指導教授-曾憲嫻
口試委員-喻肇青
口試委員-鄭泰昇
口試委員-孔憲法



關鍵字(中)
臺南府城廟境網絡分佈特性傳統街巷空間型構法則


關鍵字(英)
Tainan CityNetwork of Religious TerritoryDistributionsTraditional-AlleywaySpace Syntax


學科別分類



中文摘要
從2005年「文化資產保存法」與2006年「文化資產保存法施行細則」發佈後，臺灣開始重視文化景觀中歷史文化路徑、宗教景觀等民俗文化，試圖透過民俗文化的重視，配合規劃設計，達到文化資產價值的提升。回顧目前臺灣的保存狀況，祠廟之建物所保存的比例相當高，而這些廟宇分佈點，在往後的歷史保存上可衍伸出怎樣的空間策略思維？為本研究初期的發想。本研究深入探討祭祀圈、廟境等概念，顯示了廟宇分佈反映於傳統社會中，不單單只扮演了精神核心，在地理空間上，往上連結公共性大街，往下連結生活層級的巷弄，塑造出完整的都市架構，並藉由遶境等儀式，達到民防、交誼等意念，賦予了空間單元之生命力，因此，探究廟宇和歷史網絡的關係，為研究所關註的課題。研究操作上，將關鍵年代的圖面資料，透過向量化轉為CAD數位檔，匯入AxialGen產出軸線地圖（axial map），進行空間語法（space syntax）的分析，解析出府城廟境空間之組成單元架構，同時經由三角矯正後的疊圖，分析出其空間網絡之變動狀況。最後研究成果，主要說明突破文獻蒐集與史料分析的侷限性，釐清歷史路徑的空間定位，並且，導正目前保存，多以空間資源判定該路網價值之逆向思維，轉而，先將路網結構的定位，再疊合現存的空間資源，建立客觀的分析流程。


英文摘要
Cultural Heritage Conservation, Act, 2005 and Enforcement the Rules of Cultural Heritage Conservation Act, 2006 are published. Taiwan began to pay attention to cultural route and religious landscape in the cultural landscape, such as folk culture. Try to the attention of the local culture, with the planning design, to achieve the enhancement of Cultural Heritage of value. Review the conservation status of Taiwan, the conservation is quite high on the ratio of the temple buildings. In the future, these temple's distribution points in the preservation of the historic district extend as how space strategy thinking? That is imagination for the initial study.This study about the concept of territorial cult and network of religious territory, shows the distribution of the temple are reflected in the traditional culture, not just only the core of the spiritual dimension. The old settlements extended their network, mainly based on temple court as the core area, and the organic space formed many historical and cultural street. The spaces of temple squares, linked up not only public avenue, but also street-level life, together, create a completed urban pattern. Additionally from folk-temple festivals to old central-district revitalization, the scope of the present area from every core area.This study collects all image data of important years, then used CAD to interpret the image file to vector file. After the interpretation, import map data into AxialGen in GIS interface, then output axial map as the basis of space syntax analysis. Transformations of the religious territory in Tainan city by spatial environment are analyze by overlay GIS calibration's maps for the next phase of analysis. The final research results breakthrough the limitations of the literature collection and historical analysis to clarify the spatial orientation of the cultural route. Turn the reverse thinking of preservation that of space resources to determine the value of the road network into the road network structure positioning in first, and then superimposed the existing space resources to establish an objective analysis process.


