      第 8 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0026-1208201115114700


論文名稱(中文) 
      
薩鎮冰在清末海軍整建裡扮演的角色(1895-1911)


論文名稱(英文) 
      
The character of Sa Zhen-Bing in reconstruction of Chinese Navy at the Late Qing Dynasty（1895-1911）


校院名稱
成功大學


系所名稱(中)
歷史學系碩博士班


系所名稱(英)
Department of History


學年度
99


學期
2


出版年
100


研究生(中文)
陳致學


學號
k3697403


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2011-06-23


論文頁數
193頁


口試委員
指導教授-蘇梅芳
口試委員-鄭梓
口試委員-王明燦



關鍵字(中)
薩鎮冰象山港出洋考察籌辦海軍事務處煙臺海軍學堂


關鍵字(英)
Sa Zhen-BingXiangshan Harbourexplored abroadPre-Naval departmentYantai Navy School


學科別分類



中文摘要
   薩鎮冰出身於福州船政學堂，之後又去英國留學，歸國後先後擔任船艦管帶及教習，擁有豐富的經驗。甲午海戰以後，中國海軍遭受重創，在財政困難的情形下，海軍衙門和北洋艦隊陸續遭到裁撤，對於海軍整頓的部分，只能初步購買一些船艦，或是修建一些砲臺。    甲午戰後，薩鎮冰被免職，後來藉由張之洞的推薦，出任吳淞砲臺總臺官。光緒二十四年（1898年），由於鄭孝胥的舉薦，清廷開始重新註意到他，經過一段時間的觀察，將他升任為海軍幫統領，逐漸使其著手海軍整建的工作。光緒二十六年（1900年）的庚子事變，使得薩鎮冰的任事態度與決心受到袁世凱註意，開始提拔他主持海軍事務。    在海軍事務上，薩鎮冰的計畫分為硬體和軟體上的整頓。硬體上，他籌劃象山港的興建，還有新的艦隊編制。此外，擔任籌辦海軍大臣期間，前往歐洲及美日等國，購買船艦，逐步重整海軍；軟體上，主要體現在制度與教育上，薩鎮冰主持籌辦海軍事務處，並且參與海軍部的成立。他並成立煙臺海軍學堂，還有提出海軍大學堂的構想，積極推動出國留學的計畫。


英文摘要
     Sa Zhen-Bing has studied in Fuzhou Navy School and GreenWich College. After returning, he was a captain of the battleship and the teacher of the Navy school. Due to this, he has lots of experience. After The First Sino-Japanese War, Chinese Navy have been damaged. Because Pecuniary embarrassment, the Beiyang Fleet and Naval Ministry were been dissolved. About the reconstruction of Chinese Navy, Chinese government just bought some battleship and fixed some fort.     After The First Sino-Japanese War, Sa Zhen-Bing was removed from the office. But fortunately he was recommended by Zhang Zhi-Dong, he managed the fort of Wusong. He was recommended by Zheng Xiao-Xu in 1898, and he would managed the reconstruction of Chinese navy. Boxer Rebellion was broken out in 1900, Sa Zhen-Bing’s attitude and determination were noticed by Yuan Shi-Kai, that Yuan Shi-Kai decided to arrange him to manage Chinese Navy.     In administration of Chinese Navy, Sa Zhen-Bing’s plan included hardware and software.About the hardware, he prepared to build Xiangshan Harbour, and reconstructed  the fleet. Besides, in the period he being minister of Pre-Naval department, he went to Europe, U.S and Japan buying the battleship and equipment, gradually setting the Navy. In the software, the change mainly about the system and the education. Sa Zhen-Bing managed Pre-Naval department, and participated in the established of Naval department. He established the Yantai Navy School, and prepared to establish Navy College. He also plane to study abroad of the students of Navy positively.


論文目次
